Post content:
Realtime Sales Copilot

Stop guessing on sales calls. Know exactly what to say. TL;DR: Nomi gives you real-time sales advice during calls. See what to say, what to ask, and how to close. Plus free AI note-taking forever. You're on a sales call. The prospect asks a tough question. You freeze. Or worse, you ramble. They ask about your API limits. You're not sure. They push back on pricing. You cave too early. They want a technical deep-dive. You lose the room. Look, everyone has off days. But here's the thing - AI is everywhere now. So why are you still making these preventable mistakes? Even when calls feel great, deals die the next day. Why? Because you missed the key moment to close. Nomi listens to your calls and shows you exactly what to say. Right on your screen. As you talk. One customer went from $100K to $360K in two weeks using Nomi. He had the pipeline, we had the sales fuel. PS: Nomi is always learning. We use reinforcement learning and gradient boosting techniques to continuously improve your sales playbook and your custom model. Forget paying $50/month for meeting bots. You get: All free. Forever. Not a trial. Your data is safe. Security provided by Probo (YC X25). SOC II, GDPR ready, and CCPA ready. Ready to get more deals done? — Your job is to get deals done. Our job is to make it easy.

@Swan Beaujard
@Ethan Safar

